the weather forecast today?

363
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:17,120
Because they said it's going
to rain but it looks lovely.

364
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,580
If it has been raining a lot,

365
00:15:18,580 --> 00:15:22,570
